title: Flight Simulator 2020 - POI's - Canada - Legislative Assembly of British Columbia
description:
In this video we will fly over the Legislative Assembly of British Columbia. The Legislative Assembly of British Columbia is the deliberative assembly of the Parliament of British Columbia, in the province of British Columbia, Canada. The Legislative Assembly meets in Victoria. Members are elected from provincial ridings and are referred to as members of the Legislative Assembly (MLAs). Bills passed by the legislature are given royal assent by the Canadian monarch, represented by the Lieutenant Governor of British Columbia.
